org.apache.poi.hslf.record

Class DummyRecordWithChildren

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hslf.record.Record
      • org.apache.poi.hslf.record.RecordContainer
        • org.apache.poi.hslf.record.DummyRecordWithChildren
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    GenericRecord 

    public final class DummyRecordWithChildren
extends RecordContainer
    If we come across a record we know has children of (potential) interest, but where the record itself is boring, we create one of these. It allows us to get at the children, but not much else(如果我们遇到一张我们知道有（潜在）感兴趣的孩子的唱片，但如果唱片本身很无聊，我们就会创建其中的一张。它可以让我们接近孩子们，但仅此而已)
    Author:
    Nick Burch
